(1). TWO journal articles related to OCCUPATIONAL OR ENVIRONMENTAL OR BIOLOGICAL MONITORING published by SCI journals (in 2009 and after), must be selected and integrated to submit your reports.
(2). The articles and your reports should be collected by TA on June, 18. Scores for late reports will be less than 60 points.      

